@startuml
[*] --> Registering : enter details
Registering --> LoggedIn : register
LoggedIn --> UploadingDocuments : upload documents
LoggedIn --> ViewingProfile : view profile
LoggedIn --> ApplyingForCertificate : apply for certificate
UploadingDocuments --> UploadingDocuments : continue uploading
LoggedIn --> LoggedOut : done with actions
ApplyingForCertificate --> AppliedForCertificate : request certificate
AppliedForCertificate --> AppliedForCertificate : reapply after sending request
Registering --> LoggedIn : login if details correct
@enduml
